title: SunnyDay
description: The name of this architectural visualization project is SunnyDay and the project contains a lot of optimized resources. You can use these resources to quickly create different scenarios.
longDescription:
Video Preview:https://youtu.be/1FRB-SHufXM

The name of this architectural visualization project is SunnyDay, which contains a large number of optimized static mesh models and all contain very good lightmaps. The project's lighting uses the least amount of light and achieves excellent results. And the project contains a lot of HD map normal maps and some more practical particle effects.
technicalDetails:
